        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 11 at 6:29PM MDT until July 11 at 7:00PM MDT by NWS Pueblo CO</headline>
        <description>SVRPUB

The National Weather Service in Pueblo has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
North central Las Animas County in southeastern Colorado...

* Until 700 PM MDT.

* At 629 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 17 miles east of
Thatcher, or 31 miles south of La Junta, moving southwest at 15
mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles. Expect
wind damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

* This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of
north central Las Animas County.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
